@Splenivore


[Pillory of the Sleepless](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pillory of the Sleepless) is a gold card, requireing two colors to play. Gold cards tend to get a 'Gold Discount', having a casting cost 1 or 2 less then they would get if they were a monocolored card (3 or more for gold cards with more then 2 colors). You should have taken that discount into account when using the Pillory as a basis to identify the propper cost for this card.

In other words, B would be too low a cost. 1B would be a better cost.
